These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: apricot, yellow, ebony, brown, black, blue, lavender
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, skydiving, chess, baking, reading, video-games, magic-tricks
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, february, january, august, november, july, december
7 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, cat, guinea-pig, turtle, horse, chinchilla
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 6. the person who likes yellow is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes black##1
12. the person who likes black is the owner of the lizard##1
13. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
14. the person who's hobby is video-games is the owner of the cat##1
15. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
16. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
17. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
18. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
19. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Color      | yellow  | blue        | black | ebony      | brown     | apricot      | lavender     |
| Hobby   | skydiving | baking         | magic-tricks   | card-games | video-games    | reading | chess |
| Birthday         | january | november | april | february | december  | july  | august    |
| Pet     | turtle  | horse         | lizard     | hamster    | cat | guinea-pig     | chinchilla     |

